data.name: IssuarTxt.ToolTip
data.value:
Optional: Set issuar name of the file which will signed.
Normally this field is not necessary, but when you include the value the value must be as same as the issuar name value of the signing certificate (*.pfx,.*cer) file.

data.name: SubjectTxt.ToolTip
data.value:
Optional: Set subject name of the file which will signed.
Normally this field is not necessary, but when you include the value the value must be as same as the subject value of the signing certificate (*.pfx,.*cer) file.

data.name: TimestampCheck.ToolTip
data.value:
Optional: Set timestamp authority for the file which will signed.
This option is not necessary, but if you check it then the the file which will signed will be timestamped if the internet connection is avilable.

data.name: PasswordTxt.ToolTip
data.value:
Optional: Enter the password of certificate file (*.pfx), which is used to sign the specified file.
This field is not necessary, but if your certificate (*.pfx) has a password then you must enter the password, if not then put it blank.
